
_text = "Staying, I explore the small town around me. Its bustling with life as people from all around the world come here to gain access to the surrounding islands.\n\nThis is still one of my favourite places to gaze at the architecture and admire how it’s built within the cove. It feels almost as if the treeline is engulfing the buildings around us, making these apartment buildings much smaller than they actually are.\n\nI can’t help but think how small we are in comparison.\n\nMy memory of this place ends here"

